726399f-a.title: Queens: Cornaga Avenue - Beach 20th Street
726399f-a.text:
Cornaga Ave., north side, west from Beach 20th Street, showing Harry's Restaurant closed in preparation for its demolishment. Adjoining on the left is the property belonging to Mre. Eelly in 1891.
October 1924.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
